One bottle can be diluted down to 4 liters,sweetened the way you like,with your choice of sweetener,I like honey.I drink 16 32oz a day per doctor recommendation and have not had a bladder infection since!It keeps in the fridge for a long time.I have gone up to 3 months without issue.
